<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 21:13:48 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>马赫雷斯进球让阿尔阿赫利在亚冠联赛中保持完美</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/mahrez-strikes-keep-al-ahli-perfect-asian-champions-league-2024-09-30/</link><description>沙特阿拉伯的阿赫利队周一在亚洲冠军联赛精英赛中保持了完美的开局，里亚德·马赫雷斯和罗杰·伊巴内斯的进球帮助球队以 2-0 战胜了阿尔瓦斯尔队，而克里斯蒂亚诺·罗纳尔多则在阿尔纳赛尔队以 2-1 战胜阿尔-瓦斯尔队的比赛中进球。雷扬。</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 20:55:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/mahrez-strikes-keep-al-ahli-perfect-asian-champions-league-2024-09-30/</guid></item><item><title>由于中国的激励措施吸引了谨慎的电动汽车买家，特斯拉的季度交付量将上升</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/teslas-quarterly-deliveries-set-rise-china-incentives-lure-wary-ev-buyers-2024-09-30/</link><description>华尔街估计，在全球最大汽车市场中国的长期激励措施和利润丰厚的融资计划的推动下，特斯拉周三第三季度电动汽车交付量预计将增长 8%。</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 17:30:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/teslas-quarterly-deliveries-set-rise-china-incentives-lure-wary-ev-buyers-2024-09-30/</guid></item><item><title>科学家解释珠穆朗玛峰的异常生长</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/science/scientists-explain-mount-everests-anomalous-growth-2024-09-30/</link><description>珠穆朗玛峰是地球上最高的山峰，海拔 8.85 公里（5.5 英里），而且实际上还在不断增长。</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 17:05:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/science/scientists-explain-mount-everests-anomalous-growth-2024-09-30/</guid></item><item><title>研究小组向铜多头发出了一条发人深省的信息：Andy Home</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/study-group-has-sobering-message-copper-bulls-andy-home-2024-09-30/</link><description>由于中国承诺的经济刺激计划重新点燃了投资者的热情，本周铜价大幅上涨。</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 16:29:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/study-group-has-sobering-message-copper-bulls-andy-home-2024-09-30/</guid></item><item><title>北京放宽购房规定以刺激需求</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/beijing-eases-home-purchase-rules-boost-demand-2024-09-30/</link><description>继上海和深圳采取类似举措后，北京周一放松了购房限制，以提振需求并支撑陷入困境的房地产市场。</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 15:12:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/beijing-eases-home-purchase-rules-boost-demand-2024-09-30/</guid></item><item><title>美国联邦贸易委员会允许雪佛龙-赫斯交易，但禁止约翰·赫斯加入董事会</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/ftc-allows-chevron-hess-deal-bars-john-hess-board-2024-09-30/</link><description>美国联邦贸易委员会周一允许雪佛龙以 530 亿美元收购赫斯公司 (Hess Corp)，该命令禁止赫斯公司首席执行官约翰·赫斯 (John Hess) 进入雪佛龙董事会。</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 14:44:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/ftc-allows-chevron-hess-deal-bars-john-hess-board-2024-09-30/</guid></item><item><title>欧洲央行拉加德称赞裕信银行与德国商业银行的银行合并</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/europe-needs-bigger-banks-compete-with-us-chinese-rivals-lagarde-2024-09-30/</link><description>欧洲央行行长克里斯蒂娜·拉加德周一表示，欧洲银行之间的合并如果能帮助它们与美国和中国的竞争对手竞争，那么“值得”。意大利联合信贷银行敦促与德国商业银行结盟。</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 14:07:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/europe-needs-bigger-banks-compete-with-us-chinese-rivals-lagarde-2024-09-30/</guid></item><item><title>第三季度市场过山车般的日元刺激和漏油事件</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-q3-pix-2024-09-30/</link><description>对于市场来说，这是一个多么疯狂的季度啊！日元出现自 2008 年全球金融危机以来最强劲的走势，各国央行快速调整政策，石油价格跳水，黄金闪耀，中国推出经济刺激措施。</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 13:42:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-q3-pix-2024-09-30/</guid></item><item><title>美国制定新规则可能会刺激人工智能芯片向中东的出货量</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-sets-new-rule-that-could-spur-ai-chips-middle-east-2024-09-30/</link><description>美国商务部周一公布了一项规定，可以放宽英伟达公司等人工智能芯片向中东数据中心的运输。</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 13:32:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-sets-new-rule-that-could-spur-ai-chips-middle-east-2024-09-30/</guid></item><item><title>印度允许白米出口后全球大米价格下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/global-rice-prices-drop-after-india-allows-white-rice-exports-2024-09-30/</link><description>出口商表示，全球第一大谷物出口国印度批准恢复出口，增加了全球供应，并帮助贫穷的亚洲和非洲买家获得了更实惠的供应，全球大米价格周一下跌。</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 11:32:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/global-rice-prices-drop-after-india-allows-white-rice-exports-2024-09-30/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟表示即使在关税之后仍可能继续与中国电动汽车谈判</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-continue-china-electric-vehicle-talks-even-after-final-vote-say-sources-2024-09-30/</link><description>欧盟一位高级官员周一表示，即使在征收关税之后，欧盟委员会仍愿意继续与中国就避免对中国电动汽车征收关税的潜在协议进行谈判。</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 08:50:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-continue-china-electric-vehicle-talks-even-after-final-vote-say-sources-2024-09-30/</guid></item><item><title>中国投资者涌入股市，担心错过史诗般的反弹</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinese-investors-rush-into-stocks-fear-missing-out-epic-rally-2024-09-30/</link><description>中国股市的动物精神又回来了，投资者在北京的政策刺激下涌入股市，并担心错过一些人认为的历史性反弹。</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 07:45:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinese-investors-rush-into-stocks-fear-missing-out-epic-rally-2024-09-30/</guid></item><item><title>中国“具有里程碑意义”的消费刺激计划出台后，痛苦的政策选择迫在眉睫</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/painful-policy-choices-loom-after-chinas-monumental-consumer-stimulus-plan-2024-09-30/</link><description>中国的刺激计划旨在充实消费者的口袋，以实现2024年的增长目标，这打破了已有数十年历史的政策手册，但让家庭需求而不是投资成为发展的可持续驱动力，是一条充满艰难选择的漫长道路。</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 06:34:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/painful-policy-choices-loom-after-chinas-monumental-consumer-stimulus-plan-2024-09-30/</guid></item><item><title>刺激措施助推中国股市创2008年以来最大单日涨幅</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-stocks-set-best-month-nearly-decade-stimulus-cheer-2024-09-30/</link><description>随着投资者争先恐后地加入北京最新一系列刺激措施引发的强劲反弹，国内 A 股成交量创下历史新高。</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 05:08:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-stocks-set-best-month-nearly-decade-stimulus-cheer-2024-09-30/</guid></item><item><title>创纪录的运行将金价推向四年来最好的季度</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/gold-pulls-back-dovish-fed-sets-it-best-quarter-since-2016-2024-09-30/</link><description>周一金价下跌，在美国货币宽松和中东紧张局势加剧推动历史性上涨后稍作喘息，这使得黄金有望迎来 2020 年以来最好的季度表现。</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 04:52:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/gold-pulls-back-dovish-fed-sets-it-best-quarter-since-2016-2024-09-30/</guid></item></channel></rss>